title: DoYourData Super Eraser v5.0
description:
DoYourData Super Eraser v5.0

Improvements & New Features

Re-design the interface.
Allow users to export erasure history.
Improve data erasure speed.
Newly support to clean up internet junk files and traces.
Fix minor bugs.

Powerful data erasure software to permanently destroy & wipe data from PCs, Servers, Hard Drives and removable devices with certified data erasure technologies.

Securely & Easily Wipe Data on Hard Drive or Storage Media

DoYourData Super Eraser provides easy and secure data erasure solution to permanently erase data from PCs, hard drives, RAIDs, Servers, USB drives, memory cards, digital cameras, SD cards, external hard drives. It will permanently destroy & erase selected data, leaving no chance for data recovery, without affecting the service life of the device.

Three Data Erasure Modes to Permanently Erase Your Data

Selectively Erase Files/Folders
Selectively Erase Files/Folders
Super Eraser allows you to selectively erase the files or folders from hard drive or storage media.


Wipe Hard Drive Partition
Wipe Hard Drive Partition
Permanently wipe entire hard drive partition or storage device to erase all existing and history data.


Wipe Free Unused Disk Space
Wipe Free Disk Space
Wipe free or unused disk space to permanently erase deleted/lost data without affecting the existing data.

Official Website: http://www.doyourdata.com/data-erase-software/super-eraser.html
